#: applications/luci-app-adblock-lean/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/adblock-lean/allowlist.js:11
msgid ""
"This is useful if the blocklist urls you subscribe to block something you "
"need -- rather than having to manually pause/resume adblock-lean when you "
"need to access the domain(s), or having to switch to a more permissive "
"blocklist, you can just list the domain(s) here to ensure they don't get "
"blocked."
